 STDB (lparry@free4all.co.uk - www.free0024068.free4all.co.uk)

 Demo version. - Full version available on my web pages.(see above)

 Demo version doesn't read tooltypes, and flashes any links which do
 link to a legal position.

 First thing, make sure you have required fonts.
 (Xen/8 & FixPlain/16)

 Also for include pictures a working RGFX datatype must be installed.
 XPK-mash is nneded for the pics also.

